# midjourney-mcp — env example
#
# Canonical credential path per CLAUDE.md credential-storage rule:
#   ~/.claude/midjourney-mcp/admin.env  (chmod 600, gitignored)
#
# The client auto-loads admin.env at MCP startup. .mcp.json env block stays
# empty (no inline secrets — codified after the 2026-05-19 + 2026-05-23
# GitHub PAT leak incidents that traced to inline-token regressions).
#
# PiAPI signup: https://piapi.ai/  (PAYG starts at $0.01/imagine task; or
# Host-Your-Account at $8/seat/mo if you already have a Midjourney Pro plan).
# Create API key in the PiAPI dashboard.

PIAPI_API_KEY=

# Optional. Override base URL (only useful for mocking / testing).
# PIAPI_API_BASE=https://api.piapi.ai/api/v1

# Optional. Daily USD cap. The MCP refuses cost-incurring tools once
# cumulative spend (estimated pre-call + actual on completion) exceeds this
# in a calendar day. Default $5.00.
# MIDJOURNEY_MCP_DAILY_USD_CAP=5.00

# Optional. UTC offset (in hours) that defines what "today" means for the
# daily cap reset. Default -5. Override per-location, e.g. -8 (US Pacific
# Standard), 0 (UTC), 1 (Central European), 9 (Japan Standard). No DST
# handling; use a stable offset.
# MIDJOURNEY_MCP_TZ_OFFSET_HOURS=-5

# Optional. Override audit log + daily-spend tracker locations.
# MIDJOURNEY_MCP_AUDIT_LOG=/Users/YOU/.claude/midjourney-mcp/audit.log.jsonl
# MIDJOURNEY_MCP_SPEND_FILE=/Users/YOU/.claude/midjourney-mcp/spend.json

# Optional. Override default process_mode for imagine/variation/describe/blend.
# One of: relax | fast | turbo  (PiAPI translates these to Midjourney's plan modes).
# MIDJOURNEY_MCP_PROCESS_MODE=fast
